comments: Brogdon (IND) and Richardson (PHI) engage and disengage off-ball.
Richardson (PHI) makes contact with the ball as he simultaneously makes marginal contact with Sabonis' (IND) right arm.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that Horford (PHI) last touched the ball before it went out of bounds.
Horford (PHI) briefly has his arms around Sabonis' (IND) upper half before correcting during the inbound.
Horford (PHI) makes contact across Turner's (IND) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Horford (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in J. Holiday's (IND) path and does not deliver the contact.
Sabonis (IND) makes marginal contact with Thybulle (PHI) and doesn't affect his SQBR at the start of his drive.
Brogdon (IND) engages and disengages with Simmons (PHI) near the lane line.
J. Holiday (IND) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Simmons (PHI) before incidental contact is made thereafter.
Sabonis (IND) makes incidental contact with Simmons (PHI) as they both make natural movements toward the loose ball.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Harris (PHI) makes marginal contact with Turner's (IND) right arm during rebounding.
Richardson (PHI) makes incidental contact with Brogdon's (IND) right side/arm as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Sabonis (IND) turns and delivers contact by extending his hip into Richardson (PHI) during the pick.
Horford (PHI) makes marginal contact with Brogdon's (IND) side at the end of the drive.
Horford (PHI) initiates contact with Turner's (IND) right wrist that pulls his hand away from the ball during the rebound.
Simmons (PHI) moves into Brogdon's (IND) space and initiates contact that affects his ability to rebound.
Richardson (PHI) and J. Holiday (IND) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Richardson (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Turner's (IND) path and does not deliver the contact.
Warren (IND) cleanly blocks Harris' (PHI) jump shot attempt prior to making incidental contact.
Horford (PHI) makes marginal contact with Turner's (IND) right side/arm during rebounding.
Thybulle (PHI) commits the take foul on Brogdon (IND).
J. Holiday (IND) makes marginal contact with Simmons' (PHI) front during his drive.
Horford (PHI) firms up during the off-ball screen to Brogdon (IND) and makes marginal contact.
Simmons (PHI) commits the take foul on Sabonis (IND).
Warren (IND) and Harris (PHI) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Richardson (PHI) fails to inbound the ball within five seconds of receiving it.
Richardson (PHI) commits the take foul on Warren (PHI).
Brogdon (IND) makes marginal contact with Simmons' (PHI) side before Simmons dribbles the ball off Brogdon's knee. Brogdon does not intentionally kick the ball.
